  • public final class AccountKitGraphConstants
extends java.lang.Object
    Constants used for AccountKit graph calls and JSON processing com.facebook.accountkit.internal is solely for the use of other packages within the AccountKit SDK for Android. Use of any of the classes in this package is unsupported, and they may be modified or removed without warning at any time.
